{"tid":1494522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急求助］我擔心自己會不舉！！！","createTime":"2019-08-21T16:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T16:23:21.000Z","uid":296759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"db2c99a2e76d2bab5912cb74564a98c37e0b35f7","tid":1494522,"uid":296759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:21:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟一向係個血氣方剛有心有力嘅人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由6月9號，條鳩一路一日硬過一日！但係上星期六日開始，可能因為無食催情彈，條鳩唔知點解開始縮下縮下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係咁，鳩呢家嘢有時都唔聽話，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一旦軟咗就唔係含啜奶吹打飛機話硬就硬得返！</span><br />\n<br />\n呢排一路都係keep住睇呢兩個月儲落嘅AV(Abuse and Violence)嚟當偉哥保持硬度，希望對家淫婦一開大門就直搗黃龍。<br />\n<br />\n小弟不材，成鳩日睇鹹書，早排睇「金瓶梅」知道西門慶因為比潘金蓮控制佢<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話硬就硬話軟就軟，最終精盡人亡</span></span>。所以想請教各位爸絲，有無其他仙方J圖，可以拯救小弟，免受不舉同精盡人亡危機呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b828117af11ee52cdbfe9d2111599ca535b90215","tid":1494522,"uid":296759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"自推一下 跪求方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}